# Allowlist form (matches the upstream beads pattern): ignore everything in
# .beads/ except the committed source of truth, so new runtime files br adds
# (beads.db*, *.lock, .br_history/, daemon.*, metadata.json, .local_version,
# last-touched, *.tmp) are ignored automatically — no .gitignore churn.
*
!issues.jsonl
!config.yaml
!routes.jsonl
!.gitignore
